name: The Living Room Moleskine
description:
The Living Room Moleskine Notebook is hand-stamped using a custom-designed traditional red rubber stamp and measures 3.5 x 5.5 inches. It has 64 acid-free blank pages with the last 16 being detachable via a micro-perforated edge. Attached to the back cover is an inner pocket, perfect for storing clippings or notes.

-

Notebook comes packaged in a 5 x 7 inch 100% unbleached cotton Muslin bag with The Living Room logo stamped on it.

name: Classic Metallic Screen Print
description:
This 8x10 inch full coverage screen print was pressed with love on 140lb. Pure White French Paper using Pantone metallic blue ink and the Duke typeface. Pantone red and white lettering finish it off. 

--

Free domestic (US) shipping.

name: Hand-Stamped Muslin Bag
description: 5 x 7 hand-stamped Ampersand 100% unbleached cotton Muslin bag perfect for storing small items. Free domestic shipping (US).

name: Hand-Stamped Kraft Print
description: The Hand-Stamped Kraft Print was created using a custom-designed traditional red rubber stamp and measures 8.5 x 11 inches. It's the perfect touch for your space to tell people you're in love with design and all things ampersand. Limited run of 200 prints. Free domestic shipping (US). - Ships within 48 hours in a sturdy Kraft mailer.

name: Brady Letterpress Card
description: Printed on a 60 year old letterpress machine the Brady Letterpress Card is sure to make a statement that you are one classy beast. It features your initials, two images of your choosing and your contact information along the bottom. Printed on Crane’s Letrra 110# Cover (300 gsm) using the Raleway typeface. - Letterpress cards comes packaged in a sturdy box hand-wrapped in kraft paper tied with twine. - Crane’s Letrra 110# Cover (300 gsm) is a beautiful soft and toothy cotton stock. Sharp lines with deeper hits are held extremely well. It’s very porous as compared to other papers though 100% opacity isn’t a guarantee. - Getting ready to place an order? Please enter your Initials and requested images in the Notes to Seller section during PayPal check-out. You're also welcome to contact me directly after placing your order. Once your order has been received please allow four weeks for design, printing and delivery.

name: Helvetica Stamp
description: There's nothing like Helvetica. Stamp invitations, notecards, notebooks, artwork, client invoices, business cards or anything else you can think of with your own personalized piece of the famous typeface. The appropriate kerning adjustments will be made to leave you with a perfectly wonderful stamp. Stamp pictured is 1 x 3 inches. - Stamp comes packaged in a 5 x 7 inch 100% unbleached cotton Muslin bag. Design engraved into Maple. No handle. - Getting ready to place an order? Please enter what you'd like on the stamp (name, company name, website address or short phrase) in the Notes to Seller section during PayPal check-out. You're also welcome to contact me directly after placing your order. Once your order has been received please allow two weeks for delivery.

name: Stainless Steel iPhone Plate
description: Great for branding your company or small business this stainless steel iPhone plate sticks onto the back of your iPhone using a special removable adhesive that causes no harm to your device. Your custom artwork is etched out using a photochemical process. Stand out from the rest and show your clients and friends how cool you really are. - Available for the iPhone 4 and 4S. Shipping included in price for US and Canada. - Artwork will be obtained from you via email after placing your order within 24 hours. Just about any file type will do (.pdf .ai .eps .jpg .png .tif .gif .psd) as long as it's okay to turn the image to black and white. If you'd like something more generic (phrase, generic image, etc( we can create that for you. You'll receive a proof prior to the plate being etched.
